---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Report of a Full Flood Experience"
  description="This field report is about my first iboga full flood during the Easter treatment of Della/IBOGAGermany in April 2021 in Hesse. It is the most extraordinary experience I have had in my life so far."
  image="/images/fullflood-experience.jpg"
  locale="en"
>
  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-12">
    <header class="mb-10">
      <a href="/en/blog" class="text-forest-600 text-sm font-medium hover:text-forest-800 transition-colors">← Back to Blog</a>
      <time class="block mt-4 text-xs text-earth-400 font-medium uppercase tracking-wider">September 15, 2023</time>
      <div class="mt-2 flex gap-2">
        <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-earth-100 text-earth-600 text-xs font-medium rounded-md">Experience Report</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="mt-3 font-serif text-4xl font-semibold text-earth-900 leading-tight">
        Report of a Full Flood Experience
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-xl text-earth-600 leading-relaxed">
        This field report is about my first iboga full flood during the Easter treatment of
        Della/IBOGAGermany at the beginning of April 2021 in Hesse. It is the most extraordinary
        experience I have had in my life so far.
      </p>
      <img src="/images/fullflood-experience.jpg" alt="Full Flood Experience" class="mt-8 w-full rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-md" style="max-height: 500px; object-fit: cover;" />
    </header>

    <div class="space-y-6 text-earth-700 leading-relaxed">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold text-earth-900 mt-8">How I Found Della</h2>
      <p>
        I first came across iboga through my research into ayahuasca. Eventually I found an interview
        with Della in the Hanfmagazin and then her Facebook page. I was immediately captivated by her
        story and her work.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold text-earth-900 mt-8">The Treatment</h2>
      <p>
        At the beginning of April 2021, I travelled to Della's Easter treatment at a seminar house in
        Hesse. In addition to Della, there was Yvonne (as sitter), Marc (for the meals) and three
        other participants.
      </p>
      <p>
        The substance was filled into capsules by the participants themselves – a mixture of 2/3 Total
        Alkaloid (TA) and 1/3 HCl. Each person prepared their own dose, which felt strangely intimate
        and strengthened the intention.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold text-earth-900 mt-8">The Ingestion</h2>
      <p>
        At 14:00 it was time. We wore white clothing, lay on mattresses on the floor. Each person had
        their own sitter. The onset came after about 30–60 minutes – a tingling in the fingers and
        toes that slowly spread across the whole body.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold text-earth-900 mt-8">The Vision</h2>
      <p>
        What followed is difficult to put into words. I first saw a grey wasteland with dead trees.
        Then appeared a bell with the inscription "Psychosis" – a frightening, all-encompassing symbol.
      </p>
      <p>
        A ghostly figure – which I later called Papa Iboga – appeared with one large black eye.
        A deafening roar filled everything. I saw myself, dead, hanging from a lamppost. Then –
        Papa Iboga flipped a switch.
      </p>
      <p>
        Complete silence. Utter calm. A state I would describe as the "zero point."
      </p>

      <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-forest-400 pl-6 py-2 my-8 bg-forest-50 rounded-r-xl">
        <p class="italic text-forest-800 text-lg">
          "The zero point – no pain, no fear, no thoughts, only pure being.
          In that moment I understood what peace truly means."
        </p>
      </blockquote>

      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold text-earth-900 mt-8">Afterwards</h2>
      <p>
        After regaining motor function I felt a surge of energy, clear lungs, deep laughter.
        The rest of the week was filled with iboga leaf visions, the third eye, time travel,
        conversations with Papa Iboga.
      </p>
      <p>
        The meditative zero-point state continued for weeks after returning home.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold text-earth-900 mt-8">My Conclusion</h2>
      <p>
        It was the most extraordinary experience of my life. I wholeheartedly recommend Della and
        the treatment at IBOGAGermany. I plan to return.
      </p>
      <p>
        Iboga is not a path for everyone – but for those who are ready, it can change everything.
        You are the miracle. Iboga is just the door handle.
      </p>

      <div class="bg-earth-100 rounded-xl p-6 mt-10">
        <p class="text-earth-500 text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-wider">Disclaimer</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-earth-700 text-sm">
          This is a personal experience report. Every experience is individual.
          Iboga treatments should always be conducted with professional guidance.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-earth-100 flex justify-between items-center">
      <a href="/en/blog" class="text-forest-600 text-sm font-medium hover:text-forest-800 transition-colors">← Back to Blog</a>
      <a href="/en/treatment" class="px-4 py-2 bg-forest-600 text-white text-sm font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-forest-700 transition-colors">
        Request Treatment
      </a>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
